  "reviews": [
    {
      "text": "I recently purchased an older property that needed a fair bit of electrical work — including installing additional sockets, updating light fittings, and adding a car charger. From start to finish, Naz and Henry were absolutely fantastic. I would 100% recommend them to anyone looking for reliable, high-quality electrical work.\n\nCommunication with Naz via WhatsApp was seamless; he always responded promptly and helpfully. Henry handled much of the installation work and was consistently friendly, professional, and efficient. We’re really pleased with the end results — everything looks great and works perfectly.\n\nThanks again to both of you for making the whole process so smooth!",
      "reviewer": "Molly",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "I recently hired Naz from Amrock to run power to an outbuilding on my property, and I couldn’t be happier with the results. From start to finish, the experience was smooth and professional. He showed up on time, explained everything clearly, and made sure the job was done safely and up to regulations.\n\nThe quality of the work was excellent—clean, efficient, and exactly what I needed.\n\nHighly recommend if you need any electrical work done—reliable, friendly, and reasonably priced. Will definitely call him again for future projects!",
      "reviewer": "Faye",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Naz & Co. from Amrock installed my new electrical fire and connected it to a Fused spur through the wall.   Excellent work carried out and their rates were VERY affordable.    They even setup the fuel effect.  5* service at great prices, Highly recommend.",
      "reviewer": "Simon",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "5* service from Naz and team. Not only with the removal and fitting of a new storage heater, but also acting as intermediary between us (tenants) and landlord. Excellent communication throughout and a quick resolution. Would highly recommend.",
      "reviewer": "Rhys",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Very reliable and great to deal with. Highly recommend Naz and his team.",
      "reviewer": "JT1988JT",
      "rating": 5
    }
  ],
